                              Rainbow Writer
                              ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

ý
    This is one ultimate rainbow editor, written in AMOS by Malcolm lavery.
Everything that you could possibly think of doing to design a rainbow has
been entered into this program, including the function of making the
program as easy as possible to use.

    You can draw individual rainbow lines on the screen, ranging up to
shaded blocks. Also on the disk, comes loads of example rainbow, including
.AMOS programs which allow you to edit and use the rainbows in your own
programs. The source code for the rainbow editor also comes along with the
package. This has to be the best rainbow writer I have seen in a long time.

